      • getSourceImageId

        public String getSourceImageId()
        Returns the service-generated unique id of the image used to create this disk. This value identifies the exact image that was used to create this persistent disk. For example, if you created the persistent disk from an image that was later deleted and recreated under the same name, the source image service-generated id would identify the exact version of the image that was used.
